  "instructions": [
    "Heat the beurre-monte in an earthenware bowl over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the beef stew meat and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chilli flakes, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chopped carrots and potatoes, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the beef broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, until the vegetables are tender, about 20 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
